  â˜ 1.5) Game Progress Integration:
    â˜ Create Supabase Tables:
      - game_sessions:
        - id: uuid
        - user_id: uuid (student)
        - game_id: uuid
        - score: integer
        - duration: integer (seconds)
        - completed_at: timestamp
        - mistakes: integer
        - accuracy: float
        - level_reached: integer
      - game_progress:
        - id: uuid
        - user_id: uuid
        - game_id: uuid
        - total_score: integer
        - highest_level: integer
        - total_time: integer
        - last_played_at: timestamp
        - mastery_level: integer (1-5)
      - game_achievements:
        - id: uuid
        - user_id: uuid
        - game_id: uuid
        - achievement_id: uuid
        - earned_at: timestamp
        - progress: jsonb (specific achievement data)
    â˜ Create Progress Hooks:
      - useGameSession:
        - startSession(): Record start time
        - endSession(score, mistakes, level): Save session data
        - getRecentSessions(limit): Fetch last N sessions
      - useGameProgress:
        - updateProgress(sessionData): Update overall progress
        - getProgress(): Fetch current progress
        - getMasteryLevel(): Calculate mastery (1-5)
      - useGameAchievements:
        - checkAchievements(sessionData): Check for new achievements
        - getAchievements(): Fetch earned achievements
    â˜ Create Progress Components:
      - GameProgressBar:
        - Show current level
        - Display mastery progress
        - Visual completion status
      - AchievementDisplay:
        - Show earned achievements
        - Display progress to next achievement
        - Highlight recent achievements

